{"tha-ap92:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap92:0.2":"Timiravagga ","tha-ap92:0.3":"Padumapupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap92:1.1":"“Pokkharavanam pavittho, ","tha-ap92:1.2":"Bhanjanto padumaniham; ","tha-ap92:1.3":"Tatthaddasam phussam buddham, ","tha-ap92:1.4":"Battimsavaralakkhanam. ","tha-ap92:2.1":"Padumapuppham gahetvana, ","tha-ap92:2.2":"akase ukkhipim aham; ","tha-ap92:2.3":"Papakammam saritvana, ","tha-ap92:2.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","tha-ap92:3.1":"Pabbajitvana kayena, ","tha-ap92:3.2":"manasa samvutena ca; ","tha-ap92:3.3":"Vaciduccaritam hitva, ","tha-ap92:3.4":"ajivam parisodhayim. ","tha-ap92:4.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap92:4.2":"yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap92:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap92:4.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap92:5.1":"Padumabhasanama ca, ","tha-ap92:5.2":"attharasa mahipati; ","tha-ap92:5.3":"Attharasesu kappesu, ","tha-ap92:5.4":"atthatalisamasisum. ","tha-ap92:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap92:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap92:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap92:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma padumapupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap92:8.1":"Padumapupphiyattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap92:9.1":"Timiravaggo navamo. ","tha-ap92:10.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap92:11.1":"Timiranangalipuppha, ","tha-ap92:11.2":"nippannanjaliko adho; ","tha-ap92:11.3":"Dve ramsisanni phalado, ","tha-ap92:11.4":"saddasanni ca secako; ","tha-ap92:11.5":"Padmapupphi ca gathayo, ","tha-ap92:11.6":"chappannasa pakittita. "}